<style>
  .tog-guide { padding: 100px 0; background: #FCF8F1; }
  .tog-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 60px; max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
  .tog-title { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  
  .tog-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 30px; }
  .tog-card { background: #fff; padding: 40px; border-radius: 20px; text-align: center; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.02); }
  .tog-card__value { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: #1a1a1a; }
  .tog-card__temp { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #888; }
  .tog-card__desc { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #666; line-height: 1.6; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) { .tog-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>

<section class="tog-guide">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="tog-header">
      <h2 class="tog-title">Sleep Bag TOG Guide</h2>
      <p>TOG is a rating system that measures warmth and calculates how quickly a fabric uses heat. It is the standard for determining which sleep bag your baby should wear based on the ambient temperature in their nursery.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="tog-grid">
      <div class="tog-card" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="tog-card__value">0.5 TOG</div>
        <div class="tog-card__temp">74 - 78°F / 23 - 26°C</div>
        <p class="tog-card__desc">Ideal for summer and warm nurseries. Pair with a short sleeve bodysuit.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tog-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="tog-card__value">1.0 TOG</div>
        <div class="tog-card__temp">69 - 73°F / 21 - 23°C</div>
        <p class="tog-card__desc">Our most popular year-round rating. Perfect for air-conditioned nurseries.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tog-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
        <div class="tog-card__value">2.5 TOG</div>
        <div class="tog-card__temp">61 - 68°F / 16 - 20°C</div>
        <p class="tog-card__desc">Perfect for cold winter months and nurseries kept below 68°F.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{ "name": "TOG Guide Section", "settings": [], "presets": [{ "name": "TOG Guide Section" }] }
{% endschema %}
